{"lastModified":1764622692849,"uri":"c::8275378522::vessel::d5cca39c-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: British Virgin Islands, U.S. Virgin Islands\n\nIntroducing Serenity, a stunning 49’ catamaran launched in 2022, designed to embody the essence of Bali in every detail. Step aboard this floating paradise to discover four luxurious queen guest cabins, each offering a sanctuary of relaxation. With four well-appointed heads, guests are guaranteed convenience and privacy, enhancing their overall experience.\n\nThe fully equipped galley boasts modern appliances, including a full-sized refrigerator, catering to all your culinary needs. Outside, the solid deck features an expansive seating area and a serene lounge deck, perfect for creating cherished memories.\n\nOn the flybridge, an inviting table and lounge area await, offering panoramic views and the soothing touch of the sea breeze. Serenity's unique tilt-and-turn rear wall in the salon, when opened, seamlessly blends the interior with the exterior, creating an unmatched and unforgettable environment.\n\nReflecting Bali's unparalleled style and focus on livability, Serenity promises an extraordinary experience for all who come aboard. Those fortunate enough to sail on Serenity can expect their expectations to be exceeded, making them eager to return time and time again.","blueprint":{"name":"SERENITY 4.8","images":["/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cca39c-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bzw-2AmNx.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cca39c-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100329-gwOJXeNy_F.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cca39c-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100329-XHYSM89Hz.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cca39c-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100329-PsiYhipck9.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/med